579082d9-f835-40cd-abc4-206015a2ab18.title: <player>
579082d9-f835-40cd-abc4-206015a2ab18.text: Can you impart your wise knowledge to me, O Oracle?

eaaaa0ab-acac-477f-b7a1-59ff55d23c9e.title: Oracle
eaaaa0ab-acac-477f-b7a1-59ff55d23c9e.text:
The God Wars are over...as long as the thing they
were fighting over remains hidden.

96f9a9e6-dc44-4ded-a5fc-dd129faff60d.title: Oracle
96f9a9e6-dc44-4ded-a5fc-dd129faff60d.text: Beware the cabbage: it is both green AND leafy.

5ee6ea90-c59b-4d46-8a07-6f5762ddda4e.title: Oracle
5ee6ea90-c59b-4d46-8a07-6f5762ddda4e.text: Do not fear the dragons...fear their kin.

3d129c6d-2d57-447a-99cc-f264c4954608.title: Oracle
3d129c6d-2d57-447a-99cc-f264c4954608.text: Everyone you know will one day be dead.

fbfab38b-f391-4a24-bda3-6c13a1712eb1.title: Oracle
fbfab38b-f391-4a24-bda3-6c13a1712eb1.text: Is it time to wake up? I am not sure...

e43116f4-b3db-40da-92cc-2d1c9aecc418.title: Oracle
e43116f4-b3db-40da-92cc-2d1c9aecc418.text: Too many cooks spoil the anchovy pizza.

b6ad871d-7026-4580-92a1-bce24e908084.title: Oracle
b6ad871d-7026-4580-92a1-bce24e908084.text: Sometimes you get lucky, sometimes you don't.

ad433987-f53e-4654-a060-1261076d30f0.title: Oracle
ad433987-f53e-4654-a060-1261076d30f0.text: A woodchuck does not chuck wood.

bf3328dd-6657-46dd-a1fe-1d60e3e64d8e.title: Oracle
bf3328dd-6657-46dd-a1fe-1d60e3e64d8e.text: There are no crisps at the party.

fdb707fb-8efe-4672-9d9d-d0029daca3dd.title: Oracle
fdb707fb-8efe-4672-9d9d-d0029daca3dd.text:
If a tree falls in the forest and no one is around, then
nobody gets Woodcutting xp.

22dc48dc-a5ae-4732-9b5f-3472bdcf5774.title: Oracle
22dc48dc-a5ae-4732-9b5f-3472bdcf5774.text: Yes, I can. But I'm not going to.

5088523c-b4de-411f-b2e3-0b69584ecd5d.title: Oracle
5088523c-b4de-411f-b2e3-0b69584ecd5d.text: Many secrets are buried under this land.

d364ef3d-812b-4d69-a6d9-b003baadd4b7.title: Oracle
d364ef3d-812b-4d69-a6d9-b003baadd4b7.text: A bird in the hand can make a tasty snack.

68912510-25a6-44ae-905a-fe13930dd9fd.title: Oracle
68912510-25a6-44ae-905a-fe13930dd9fd.text: The chicken came before the egg.

ddbf1faa-d482-4914-9f73-2a24a9072828.title: Oracle
ddbf1faa-d482-4914-9f73-2a24a9072828.text:
He who uses the power of custard mixes it with his
tears.

d1eba968-0c26-4152-92a1-d06fbef434c7.title: Oracle
d1eba968-0c26-4152-92a1-d06fbef434c7.text:
The great snake of Guthix guards more than she
knows.

baed3ab4-fc50-4161-9920-fbbec9a440d2.title: Oracle
baed3ab4-fc50-4161-9920-fbbec9a440d2.text:
An answer is unimportant; it is the question that
matters.

eb152f65-aa18-4780-8919-a9e0eee3308a.title: Oracle
eb152f65-aa18-4780-8919-a9e0eee3308a.text:
They say that ham does not mix well with other kinds
of meat.

9aa6e4af-258c-49bb-aa31-dd46d5688546.title: Oracle
9aa6e4af-258c-49bb-aa31-dd46d5688546.text: When in Asgarnia, do as the Asgarnians do.

ab177be4-aeba-4118-8e0c-0712f9f9ee43.title: Oracle
ab177be4-aeba-4118-8e0c-0712f9f9ee43.text: No. I'm not in the mood.

48459213-a027-4d50-baf2-4ac6a91aa9e6.title: Oracle
48459213-a027-4d50-baf2-4ac6a91aa9e6.text:
The light at the end of the tunnel is the demon-infested
lava pit.

7dbaa445-c8d8-4456-a088-d176c84fd6bf.title: Oracle
7dbaa445-c8d8-4456-a088-d176c84fd6bf.text:
The goblins will never make up their minds on their
own.

330a2fa5-fb40-4c73-8bbb-1114eedf35f5.title: Oracle
330a2fa5-fb40-4c73-8bbb-1114eedf35f5.text:
Don't judge a book by its cover -  judge it on its'
grammar and, punctuation.
